# Journal

Daily notes (reading, ideas, progress). Newest first.


keep


<ul>
  {% assign entries = site.journal | sort: "date" | reverse %}
  {% for e in entries %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ e.url | relative_url }}">
        {{ e.date | date: "%Y-%m-%d" }} — {{ e.title | default: "Entry" }}
      </a>
      {% if e.tags %}<small> ({{ e.tags | join: ", " }})</small>{% endif %}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
